coalsimr 0.1
------------

* Imported coalescent simulation functionality from package jaatha.
* Redesigned the user interface using S3 and R6 classes (#1, #2, #5, #6).
* Added a caching mechanism for simulation commands (#7).
* Re-enabled bulk simulation for seq-gen (#8, #10).
* Redesigned the summary statistics system in a modular way (#17).
* Added the following summary statistics: 
  + Segregating Sites
  + Site Frequency Spectrum (SFS)
  + Joint Site Frequency Spectrum (JSFS)
